GIVEN an employee with pay type of hourly
earning 10$/hour
and with 40 hours of time-cards
and pay disposition of paymaster
and today is friday

WHEN I run payroll

THEN the paymaster should have a check for 400$.

----------------------------------------------

GIVEN an employee with standard hourly rate
and with time-cards under overtime
and pay disposition of paymaster
and today is payday

WHEN I run payroll

THEN the paymaster should have a check for hWorked*StdHourlyRate.

